`{S} {ident : InternalPort Nat} {n : Nat} {f : Fin n → RelIO S} : AssocList.contains ident (RelIO.liftFinf n f) = true → ∃ i, ident = ↑i`.

The hypothesis is `h : AssocList.contains ident (RelIO.liftFinf n f) = true`.
The goal is `∃ i : Fin n, ident = ↑i`.

